data.description: Truly a singular opportunity to own this extremely well built, spacious and classy home in one of the most desirable gated communities, Stoneybrook at Venice. This beautiful home is located within minutes drive from the Historic Downtown Venice, restaurants and convenience shops including the gorgeous Venice Beach and Pier, not forgetting to mention the amazing parks like Downtown Wallen and Cool Today Park. Stoneybrook at Venice offers an irresistible resort style living with a state of the art clubhouse, fitness center, tennis courts, baseball, basketball, junior size olympic pool, splash pool, hot tub, media & movie room, including lush nature trails to explore if you are a nature lover!  This 4 Bedroom/3 Bathroom/3 Car Garage beautiful home's Open Floor Plan concept allows a perfect and elegant flow throughout while offering plenty of light and beautiful views of the lush Preserve and peaceful Lake as you get to the backyard and covered porch.  One of the many great upgrades this home has received includes ceramic tile throughout, latest LG appliances, Samsung washer and dryer, new AC, window shutters, gorgeous light fixtures, drapes, granite countertops and much more.   If you are ready to enjoy Stoneybrook at Venice's resort life style or to make a great investment for the future, please request a private showing today.
